creator: xw infotec
descriptionHtml:
Khmer Vietnamese Translate application is perfect to translate texts fast in your phone or tablet.
You can use a word, phrase or sentence for translation.
Fast access and immediate translation.
You can use this apps as a Khmer to Vietnamese dictionary or Vietnamese to Khmer Dictionary too.
With this online translator you won't have communication problems.
You are able to translate words and even sentences, in just a split second.
The use of this app is completely free, but you need an Internet connection (3G, 4G, LTE, Wi-Fi) to connect to the server service.
share your translation via social networks (Facebook, Twitter, WhatsApp, Instagram) or SMS, Bluetooth, Email, or Wi-Fi.
This app is designed for friendly user interface



- voice input for text available.
- Integrated copy-paste functionality
- Text to speech - Hear a native speaker’s pronunciation for translated text
- Ability to search your history for recently-used expressions or translations.
- Ability to search your Favourite expressions or translation by using Favourite option.
